The  Story
Bowigens Beer Company was founded in 2015 by longtime friends Bobby Bowen and Kevin Wigen. After years of honing their creativity in the east coast music scene, they decided to channel their passions into a new venture: craft brewing.
We are a  Florida craft brewery renowned for its diverse range of award-winning beers, including IPAs, rich stouts, innovative sours, crisp lagers, and unique culinary inspired creations. We are artistic brewers who are serious about our craft but don't believe in limitations.  We combine both art and science to create high-quality beers. Whether you’re a seasoned beer connoisseurs or a craft beer novice, we’re excited to help you explore the world of craft beer and help ‘Recraft Perceptions’.
